r]]'' (Russia)\n*''[[Nowe Ksi\u0105\u017cki]]'' (Poland)\n*''[[Nyugat]]'' (Hungary, defunct?)\n}}\n\n===O===\n{{columns-list|colwidth=30em|\n*''[[Odra (magazine)|Odra]]'' (Poland)\n*''[[Okno (Russian magazine)|Okno]]'' (1923\u20131924; 2007\u2013current, Russia)\n* ''[[Oktyabr (magazine)|Oktyabr]]'' (1924\u2013current; Russia)\n*''[[One cool word]]'' (Canada)\n*''[[One Story]]'' (2002\u2013current)\n*''[[One Throne Magazine]]'' (Canada, online)\n*''[[Opium Magazine]]'' (online, 2001\u2013current)\n*''[[Orion (magazine)|Orion]]''\n*''[[Overland (magazine)|Overland]]'' (1954\u2013current, Australia)\n*''[[Owen Wister Review]]'' (1978\u2013current)\n*''[[Oxford American]]'' (1992\u2013current)\n*''[[The Oxonian Review]]'' (United Kingdom, 2001\u2013current)\n}}\n\n===P===\n{{columns-list|colwidth=30em|\n*''[[P. N. Review]]'' (United Kingdom)\n*''[[The Paris Review]]''\n*''[[Parnassus (literary magazine)|Parnassus]]'' (1965\u2013current)\n*''[[Parting Gifts (journal)|Parting Gifts]]''\n*''[[PEN America (journal)|PEN America]]''\n*''[[Perigee: Publication for the Arts]]'' (online)\n*''[[Permafrost: Literary Journal|Permafrost]]''\n*''[[Pessoa (magazine)|Pessoa]]'' (online, Brazil, 2010\u2013current)\n*''[[Phoebe (magazine)|Phoebe]]'' (1971\u2013current)\n*''[[Pinball (journal)|Pinball]]'' (2012\u2013current)\n*''[[The Pinch]]''\n*''[[Playboy]]'' (1953\u2013current)\n*''[[Pleiades (journal)|Pleiades]]''\n*''[[Ploughshares]]''\n*''[[Poesia (magazine)|Poesia]]''\n*''[[Poetry (magazine)|Poetry]]'' (1912\u2013current)\n*''[[Poetry International (magazine)|Poetry International]]'' (1997\u2013current)\n*''[[Poetry Ireland Review]]'' (Ireland)\n*''[[Poetry Kanto]]'' (Japan, 1968\u2013current)\n*''[[Poetry Review]]'' (United Kingdom)\n*''[[Poetry Wales]]'' (1965\u2013current)\n*''[[Polja (literary magazine)|Polja]]'' (Serbia)\n*''[[Post Road (magazine)|Post Road]]''\n*''[[Potomac Review]]''\n*''[[Prairie Fire (magazine)|Prairie Fire]]'' (Canada)\n*''[[Prairie Schooner]]'' (1926\u