zyhorse (magazine)|Crazyhorse]]''\n*''[[Creative Nonfiction (magazine)|Creative Nonfiction]]''\n*''[[Cricket (magazine)|Cricket]]'' (1973\u2013current)\n*''[[CutBank]]''\n*''[[Cyphers (magazine)|Cyphers]]'' (Ireland)\n}}\n\n===D===\n{{columns-list|colwidth=30em|\n*''[[December (magazine)|December]]''  (1958\u2013current)\n*''[[Dehak - A Magazine For Good Literature]] (2011\u2013current)\n*''[[Denver Quarterly]]'' (1966\u2013current)\n*''[[Desh (magazine)|Desh]]'' (Bengali, India)\n*''[[Dialog (magazine)|Dialog]]'' (Poland)\n*''[[The Dorchester Review]]'' (Canada)\n*''[[The Drouth]]'' (United Kingdom)\n*''[[Dublin Review of Books]]'' (2007\u2013current, Ireland)\n*''[[Dunes Review]]''\n*''[[Dusie]]'' (online, Switzerland)\n}}\n\n===E===\n{{columns-list|colwidth=30em|\n*''[[Eclectica Magazine]]'' (online)\n*''[[Edinburgh Review]]''\n*''[[Emerson Review]]''\n*''[[Enkare Review]]''\n*''[[Epoch (American magazine)|Epoch]]''\n*''[[Esprit (magazine)|Esprit]]'' (France)\n*''[[Evergreen Review]]'' (online)\n*''[[Existere]]'' (Canada)\n}}\n\n===F===\n{{columns-list|colwidth=30em|\n*''[[Fantastyka]]'' (Poland)\n*''[[Fence (magazine)|Fence]]''\n*''[[Fiction (magazine)|Fiction]]''\n*''[[Fiction Weekly]]'' (online)\n*''[[The Fiddlehead]]'' (Canada)\n*''[[FIELD (magazine)|FIELD]]''\n*''[[Fifth Wednesday Journal]]'' (2007\u2013current)\n*''[[Fine Madness]]'' (1982\u20132004)\n*''[[Fireweed (periodical)|Fireweed]]'' (Canada, defunct?)\n*''[[The First Line (magazine)|The First Line]]'' (1999\u2013current)\n*''[[The Florida Review]]'' (1972\u2013current)\n*''[[Flock (literary journal)|Flock]]''\n*''[[Flyway (magazine)|Flyway]]''\n*''[[Folio (magazine)|Folio]]'' (1985\u2013current)\n*''[[Fourteen Hills]]'' (1994\u2013current)\n*''[[Fugue (magazine)|Fugue]]''\n}}\n\n===G===\n{{columns-list|colwidth=30em|\n*''[[Gangway (magazine)|Gangway]]'' (Australia)\n*''[[Gargoyle Magazine]]'' (1976\u2013present)\n*''[[Geist (magazine)|Geist]]'' (Canada)\n*''[[Georgetown Review]]''\n*''[[Georgia Revi